Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.33,0:01:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,泪雨的终结
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.63,0:01:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:01:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的特别
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.58,0:01:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在这个样子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.83,0:02:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没有会输的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.03,0:03:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解放状态持续时间过长的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.83,0:03:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体就会渐渐地被咒印给侵蚀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦被侵蚀了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.73,0:04:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会永远失去自我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.13,0:04:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这副身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来已经没时间再磨磨蹭蹭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左手的感觉…消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.23,0:04:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的这股力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎也伴随着风险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.53,0:04:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被称做终结之谷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以此为舞台不是正合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.53,0:05:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过闲聊已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.73,0:05:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那差不多也该做个终结了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,0:05:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到现在为止的战斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面是第七班
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漩涡鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春野樱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.43,0:05:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和鸣人在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 宇智波佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.43,0:05:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和佐助在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少别拖我的后腿哦 废物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.73,0:05:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为因为因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师你说过啊 所以这家伙才…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是三人小组吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.53,0:06:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 我们三个是一个集体啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.33,0:06:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没受伤吧 胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没受伤吧 胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想和你战斗一场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.63,0:06:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.23,0:06:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…想要和你战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不想眼睁睁地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着重要的同伴死去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通灵之术
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.23,0:06:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小樱…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.13,0:06:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来保护
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:07:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是笑呢 是兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到能跟你在这里决斗并且取胜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.70,0:07:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖后腿的居然也如此狂妄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.13,0:07:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不会一辈子都当拖后腿的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.83,0:07:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点出招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交手之前 把护额戴上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.53,0:07:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.53,0:07:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了 快点戴上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没有本事弄伤我的额头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们作为木叶忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.53,0:07:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对等决斗的标志
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对要赢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少自以为是了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今往后…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.23,0:08:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.03,0:08:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鸟 螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鸟 螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这股查克拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气味不会消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.25,0:14:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很近了 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.85,0:14:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是来迟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.05,0:15:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.75,0:15:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是佐助的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.15,0:15:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能及时赶到 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定拼尽了全力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.95,0:16:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我在一起的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.44,0:17:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸总是会提到你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我是独一无二的兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.55,0:17:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为你必须超越的壁垒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会和你一起共存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使被你憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也和我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是万花筒写轮眼的开眼者之一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那需要特殊的条件
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀掉自己最亲密的…朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终结之谷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人和佐助竟然在这里战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.85,0:18:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真够讽刺的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.75,0:18:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着这条河流
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛让我目睹了一场永无止尽的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像建造了木叶村
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.51,0:18:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化身为这两尊石像的人的命运一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人和佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.45,0:18:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要这两人一息尚存…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:19:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀掉自己最亲密的…朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不会按你说的去做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用自己的方法获得力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用自己的方法…超越你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.25,0:19:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨…停了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这骤雨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭气味已经无法追踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 比起去追佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.33,0:20:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是鸣人更为优先吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情变得有趣起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.30,0:22:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.70,0:22:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.90,0:22:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过会把佐助带回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.30,0:22:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一生的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.30,0:22:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 一切都还没有结束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.30,0:22:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会信守约定的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.30,0:22:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是常说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.40,0:22:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一向言出必行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.30,0:23:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这就是我的忍道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.80,0:23:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.57,0:23:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未能信守的约定